# Copilot Instructions — Workshop Repository

## Repository Overview

This repository is a workshop that uses the `shinyay/workshop-pages-theme` Jekyll remote theme for GitHub Pages. The workshop is about: {WORKSHOP_DESCRIPTION}

All layouts, includes, stylesheets, and JavaScript are provided by the remote theme. This repository only contains configuration, content pages, and (optionally) sample application code for hands-on exercises.

---

## Theme Activation

The remote theme is activated through two settings in `_config.yml`:

```yaml
remote_theme: shinyay/workshop-pages-theme
plugins:
  - jekyll-remote-theme
```

Do **not** copy theme layouts, includes, SCSS, or JS files into this repository. The `jekyll-remote-theme` plugin fetches them automatically at build time.

---

## Configuration Reference

The full `_config.yml` structure for this workshop:

```yaml
remote_theme: shinyay/workshop-pages-theme

title: "{WORKSHOP_TITLE}"
description: "{DESCRIPTION}"
author: "shinyay"

plugins:
  - jekyll-remote-theme

workshop:
  category: "{CATEGORY}"        # copilot-ai | github-platform | ai-ml | cloud-infra | spring-java | devops-containers | legacy-modernization | general
  language: "{LANGUAGE}"         # e.g., Python, TypeScript, Java, Go
  difficulty: "{DIFFICULTY}"     # Beginner | Intermediate | Advanced
  duration: "{DURATION}"         # e.g., "2-3 hours"
  prerequisites:
    - "{PREREQ_1}"
    - "{PREREQ_2}"
  hub_url: "https://shinyay.github.io/awesome-shinyay-workshop/"
  show_toc: true
  show_progress: true

defaults:
  - scope:
      path: ""
    values:
      layout: "workshop"
```

### Configuration Fields

| Field | Required | Description |
|-------|----------|-------------|
| `remote_theme` | Yes | Must be `shinyay/workshop-pages-theme` |
| `title` | Yes | Workshop title shown in the header and browser tab |
| `description` | Yes | Short description for SEO and the landing page |
| `workshop.category` | Yes | Controls the header gradient color scheme |
| `workshop.language` | No | Primary programming language used in exercises |
| `workshop.difficulty` | Yes | One of `Beginner`, `Intermediate`, or `Advanced` |
| `workshop.duration` | Yes | Estimated completion time (e.g., `"2-3 hours"`) |
| `workshop.prerequisites` | No | List of prerequisite skills or tools |
| `workshop.hub_url` | No | URL back to the workshop hub |
| `workshop.show_toc` | No | Show table of contents on step pages (default `true`) |
| `workshop.show_progress` | No | Enable progress tracking (default `true`) |

