## Design Features Available

The `workshop-pages-theme` provides these features automatically — no extra configuration needed:

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Animated gradient header** | Color scheme is determined by the `category` field in `_config.yml` |
| **Copilot sparkle animations** | Decorative SVG sparkle effects in the header area |
| **Auto-generated table of contents** | Built from headings on step pages when `show_toc: true` |
| **Code copy buttons** | Automatically added to every fenced code block |
| **Language labels** | Displayed on code blocks based on the language identifier |
| **Progress tracking** | Tracks completed steps via `localStorage` when `show_progress: true` |
| **Keyboard navigation** | Use `←` and `→` arrow keys to move between steps |
| **Light / dark mode toggle** | Theme switcher in the header; respects system preference by default |
| **Mobile-responsive sidebar** | Collapsible sidebar navigation for smaller screens |
| **Print-friendly stylesheet** | Clean print layout with hidden navigation elements |
